11 SECTION 3. Section 131 of said chapter 140, as so appearing, is hereby amended in
12 subsection (h) by inserting after the word “information”, in line 272, the following words:– or
13 who fails to annually notify the licensing authority pursuant to subsection (l).
14 SECTION 4. Said section 131, as so appearing, is hereby further amended in subsection
15 (l) by adding the following sentence:– The holder of each such license to carry a firearm shall
16 annually verify by written notice, in the form of a sworn affidavit or declaration to the licensing
17 authority that issued such license, that the license holder has not lost a firearm or had a firearm
18 stolen from the license holder's possession since the date of the license holder's last renewal or
19 issuance.
